Natives to Gehenna, these are petty, sadistic, and voracious fiends. The only force that motivates them is the gnawing pain of hunger they can never satiate. They appear as a hideous, waddling blob of hairy flesh, vaguely humanoid in shape. 

      Sources:&nbsp;
    
            
                    Monster Manual II (3.0)        
              
                    Planescape Appendix 2        
              
                    Outer Planes